revision 1.3366
date: 2010/04/29 03:52:51;  author: pfaedit;  state: Exp;  lines: +2 -2
Add two python methods:
  contour.similar
  layer.similar
which allow you to compare two contours (or layers) and specify an error bound on how far they may diverge.
----------------------------
