revision 1.3076
date: 2009/02/23 15:49:27;  author: pfaedit;  state: Exp;  lines: +3 -3
If a CID font contained a ".notdef" glyph, then when FF generated a Type1 CID font resource from it, FF would omit the .notdef glyph.
