revision 1.168
date: 2004/06/18 13:13:41;  author: pfaedit;  state: Exp;  lines: +3 -3
Add three new problems to find:
   Glyphs with intersecting contours
   Multiple glyphs with same name
   Multiple glyphs with same unicode code point
