revision 1.1718.2.1
date: 2007/03/15 13:11:59;  author: pfaedit;  state: Exp;  lines: +3 -3
Output/Input of Apple's 'lcar' table wasn't consistent. Hardly surprising as it isn't too well documented and I have no examples.
